# Sample .gitignore for an Odoo project whose local runtime/validation harness lives
# INSIDE the working tree (the real jw_dev layout: `.../99. odoo/00. DATA/`).
# Copy these lines into the project's own .gitignore (per-clone, like git-tier/.gitattributes.sample).
#
# WHY: `00. DATA/` holds the multi-GB Odoo community/enterprise sources, the harness, the
# regenerable warm base, and warm-pass caches (see validation-harness/README.md,
# WORKFLOW.md). It is runtime material, NOT a commit target. Left un-ignored, git has to
# enumerate those GBs on every `git status` / untracked scan, a confirmed root cause of
# slow load-time on `/mnt/z`. Ignoring it keeps `git status` fast.
#
# The trailing-slash, unanchored patterns match the runtime dir at ANY depth, so this works
# whether the git root is at `99. odoo/` or a parent.

# Odoo local runtime/source + harness (community/enterprise sources, harness, warm base)
00. DATA/

# Warm-PASS validation caches, wherever the harness writes them
.warm-pass-cache.*/
